    "title": "neuromorphic memory optimization",
    "description": "This project explores memory-efficient neuromorphic accelerator design by analyzing and optimizing synaptic weight storage and access patterns. It includes hardware\u2013software co-design using Verilog and Python, weight quantization (8/16/32-bit), access tracing, visualization, and accuracy\u2013memory trade-off evaluation for spiking neural networks.",
